Author: WisePassICO
Title: [ANN][ICO][WisePass] - Lifestyle Cryptocurrency Platform
Body: WisePass - Lifestyle Cryptocurrency Platform  Website / Telegram  Token Sale Starts June 10, 2018  About WisePass - WisePass is a subscription-based lifestyle platform offering members entitlements to free lunch, dinner, coffee, spirits & wine, and other lifestyle services at our world-class and local 5-star partner venues. Wisepass has a core mission statement to build a genuine relationship between brands and consumers through mobile. With PASS, token holders will be able to get enormous discounts on the monthly service as well as be able to make purchases at WisePass’ certified merchants.  Proven Track Record  Established in 2014, WisePass has grown steadily with a 60% increase in revenue for the past 7 quarters. With over 500 members and nearly 200 partner venues across 3 countries, WisePass has driven more than 20,000 visits to its sub-merchant venues to date.  Successfully Raised VC Investments  In 2016, WisePass partnered with the Vietnamese accelerator VIISA. The following year, after a meticulous inspection process, WisePass was awarded a generous seed fund from the Singapore-based venture capital firm Expara Ventures. As a result of this affiliation, WisePass has connected with numerous dynamic and reputable investors who continuously show great interest. The latest investors to come onboard have tripled the company’s valuation and is a former executive of Uber Singapore.  Enormous Potential  As a utility token, PASS is rather unique in that our existing partnerships and agreements with world-class and local venues across South East Asia lay the foundation for the implementation of this technology to be not only successful but inevitable.  Our Mission  WisePass is focused on successfully bridging the gap between the crypto and real world. We believe our platform is tailor-made to transcend the two and provide the path of least resistance in building this connection. We trust in the power of blockchain to not only increase reliable, transparent data exchange between suppliers and distributors but also between merchants and their consumers. By utilizing cryptocurrencies to purchase everyday lifestyle goods and services at WisePass certified merchants, token holders will have the ability to utilize their crypto the same as any ordinary fiat currency. This will leverage the decentralized component of the blockchain technology and revolutionize how crypto is used in everyday life.  Problems  Applications which partner with the HORECA and nightlife industries almost universally charge a commission or a fee for the establishments using their platform. This is often their primary revenue stream and eats up the partners margins and negatively affects the long-term business relationship.  Brands selling in the HORECA and nightlife sectors have trouble accurately measuring the effectiveness of their marketing campaigns. Not only is the information provided by the F&B manager of a venue typically inadequate, there are incentives for them to give a low estimation as this will result in an increase in funding.  Visiting a big city can be overwhelming as the wealth of options are often immense. It is often difficult to narrow down quality F&B options to fit specific tastes and this results in visitors compromising with convenience over quality.  Travelling can be a costly endeavor and crossing borders typically requires travellers to visit currency exchange offices which charge massive service fees due to the lack of related alternatives.  There has yet to be a successful implementation of cryptocurrency applied in real world contexts. There are many ICOs focusing on the technology but neglecting the supply side of the equation. Crypto-holders are still not able to use their resources to purchase everyday lifestyle goods and services.  Solutions  WisePass doesn’t charge partners commission and instead uses alternative streams of revenue, this helps to preserve the partners margins, increase WisePass’ profit potential and ensures that the relationship is mutually beneficial. We also buy directly from the partner venue or brand supplier and therefore ensure our customers receive exactly what they want. By building and maintaining a strong relationship with both parties, sustainability is more easily realized.  With WisePass adopting blockchain ledger, our partner brands such as Moet-Hennessy will find comfort in the consistent reliable nature of the transaction data recorded. Multiple levels of the supply chain in the HORECA industry will be required to record accurate and fixed data, revolutionizing the poorly designed data capture methods typically used today. With blockchain technology much of the mistake-prone human side of the data input process will be removed in favour of smart assets, and direct measurement tools. Partner brands will be able to know with complete accuracy who the buyer is, which bottles are most popular, what day, and even the hour their product is most often consumed, providing a guaranteed, quantifiable ROI quickly and across multiple countries and markets.  With WisePass, an upcoming update to the app will offer an AI-driven personalized recommendation system unique for every user based on their user history, time of day, gender, age, location and purpose, and other relevant details. These data points will be used to ensure the most relevant options appear first to the end user in any city they end up in where WisePass is offered. As the user base grows and gets updated daily in real-time, Wisepass will become indispensable as a lifestyle tool for the modern man or woman.  PASS token holders will be able to use the tokens across borders in universal contexts regardless of the country. PASS users will be able to travel and purchase as they wish without losing their hard earned money to high service fees charged by currency exchange offices.  Wisepass is currently focused on creating the supply - the necessary business development needs. This is our primary focus at the moment as we utilize our existing technology for the time being before we begin implementing our developments in large scale systems. Since we are buying products and services directly from our partners using either fiat or cryptocurrencies, our users are given a guarantee that their purchases will be accepted.  Technology  Here at WisePass, we’re convinced that blockchain technology with smart contracts is the future for the supply chain in the HORECA industry. With the immutable blockchain ledger, we will be able to access more reliable data regarding inventory exchange with our merchant venues and can reliably store our market data, analytics and reports on-chain.  Why WisePass  Our subscription service has long been established and proven to be a successful and scalable platform within the lifestyle industry. Unlike many other blockchain startups, we have a profitable business with tangible results that can be seen in the here and now. We have a number of high-profile partnerships with world-class brands and a loyal clientele. WisePass has a solid track record and high-profile industry leaders agree when talking about WisePass that “when it comes to lifestyle platforms, the implementation of crypto-technology to automate, digitize, and decentralize the process seems to be a natural transition.”  200+ Partner Venues | 4 Cities | 3 Countries | 20,000 Visits  Token Sale  PASS Token is our proprietary cryptocurrency designed to facilitate a standardized global approach to the long-term rental process, with all transactions kept in a secure manner.
